1. AI-Powered Presentation Generation – Gamma AI

Problem Statement

Traditional presentation creation involves:

Content ideation

Slide structuring

Visual formatting

Design alignment


This process is time-intensive and requires design skills.

Solution

Gamma AI automates presentation design and content structuring using prompt-based generation.

Implementation Steps

1. Create an account on Gamma AI.


2. Select “Generate” option.


3. Provide a structured prompt.


4. Review and refine generated slides.


5. Customize layout, theme, and visuals.



Example Prompt

Create a presentation on Generative AI.
Target audience: Undergraduate engineering students.
Tone: Professional and beginner-friendly.
Include real-world applications and future scope.

Key Benefits

Reduces presentation development time from hours to minutes

Automatically applies professional design principles

Allows focus on content quality instead of formatting

Suitable for academic seminars and corporate presentations


