4. Prompt Engineering Fundamentals

Prompt quality directly influences AI output quality. Structured prompts lead to precise, contextual, and actionable responses.

Effective Prompt Framework

1. Define the Role


2. Specify the Task


3. Provide Context


4. Define Output Format


5. Add Constraints



Example Comparison

Weak Prompt
Explain Generative AI.

Structured Prompt
Act as an AI professor.
Explain Generative AI to a second-year B.Tech student.
Use real-world examples and bullet points.
Limit response to 300 words.

Outcome

Improved clarity

Reduced ambiguity

More relevant responses

Enterprise-level output quality





